				<td colspan="2"><span>Zone Exp Modifiers (ZEM) are across the whole zone and for anyone in them.  The levels listed are simply to give people a feeling for who should hunt there. 
<br />

<br />
Based on that, and an increase in teh ZEM, you could probably hunt in Hate's Fury at 65, for xp, but I would guess that it's still not that great of xp, since the mob levels aren't high, relative to your level.  For characters 51 and over, there is a huge xp bonus for fighting stuff above your level. 
<br />

<br />
Wyndaria.
<br />
