				<td colspan="2"><span>Personally, I think it's a good thing.
<br />

<br />
Not only will it get people to different zones (If they move the &quot;hot spot&quot; zones from time to time as they say.) but also....frankly....the 1-50 or even the 1-64 game is just a joke now. No reason not to speed up the leveling a bit now. There's no newbies anymore. 
<br />

<br />
I've been playing for...d*mn...5 years I think? I don't want to level a class from 1 to 65 anymore. I might want to try out a different class, but it's just boring. There's no content at low levels anymore, just mind numbingly boring xp grinding.
<br />

<br />
So yeah. I'm sure some will complain about how, &quot;SOE is making is so easy for newbies nowadays!!&quot; but let's face it. The game is aging. There are no newbies anymore. 1-64 is a joke now. I don't wanna see instant level 65 chars, but speeding up the process a bit can't hurt.</span></td>
